name: Quest 4 Violence "Anatomy of a Hostile Mind"
description:
"Duotone" Pure Gold Metallic and Black fine halftone screen print onto  heavy weight Velin BFK 250 GSM. This fine printmaking paper is mould-made with a pronounced grain and has a lightly textured, absorbent surface. Velin BFK paper is made of 100% cotton, is acid free, soft-sized and buffered. Each sheet has two natural deckles and two tear deckled edges.
Poster size 385w x 570h mm
